5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games | gardening | board-games | writing | puzzles | reading |

